# VEHICLE::SET_SCRIPT_ROCKET_BOOST_RECHARGE_TIME

## Summary
Sets the time it takes to recharge the rocket boost

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **FLOAT** rechargeTime
